utation time for TBMEs, by a factor of about 30, as compared with our\nprevious code that uses two-dimensional integrals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2012 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-06"}
