blem at low redshifts, when the physical processes\nincluded provide a realistic description of cooling in the central regions of\ngalaxy clusters. [Abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2012 20:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
