 to rich possibilities\nfor manipulating spin and valley degrees of freedom in these atomically thin 2D\nmaterials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2012 08:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-17"}
